<title>SOUTH AFRICA: PUBLICO YR HEADLINE SHR SLIPS, DIV CUT.</title>
<headline>PUBLICO YR HEADLINE SHR SLIPS, DIV CUT.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended February 28</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)	 </p>
<p>    Shr, (cts)	 </p>
<p>    - headline		 14.6	  vs     26.1</p>
<p>    - attrib		   25.8	  vs     26.1</p>
<p>    Div (cts)		   3.0	  vs     6.0  </p>
<p>    Attrib income	    2.93	  vs     2.38</p>
<p>    Pre-tax		    3.64	  vs     3.90</p>
<p>    Tax			  0.09 gain   vs     0.88 paid</p>
<p>    Finance costs	    0.82	  vs     0.34</p>
<p>    Turnover		  55.54	  vs     54.12</p>
<p>    Exceptional items	3.14 gain   vs     nil  </p>
<p>    Share of associates'   0.51 gain   vs     0.14 loss </p>
<p>Div payable July 18</p>
<p>on register June 6</p>
<p>Full name: Publico Ltd (media)</p>
<p>NOTE - The company said pre-tax profit declined largely due</p>
<p>to losses in the information technology titles division. </p>
<p>It said its focus on broadcasting will continue to have a</p>
<p>positive impact on profitability during the current year. </p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
